					<description><![CDATA[<p>December 21st, 2006 is when I turned in my key card at Neteller, stepping down as lead architect, to begin working with a group that would eventually form the majority of what Redfall Technologies Inc is today. Over the last 7 years I&#8217;ve had the opportunity to work with tremendous people doing what I enjoy. [&#8230;]</p>
<p>The post <a href="https://stancarney.co/2014/01/functionredfall_technologies-vogogo-next/">function([&#8216;redfall&#8217;, &#8216;vogogo&#8217;], next) { //&#8230; };</a> appeared first on <a href="https://stancarney.co">Stan Carney</a>.</p>
