										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>December 21st, 2006 is when I turned in my key card at Neteller, stepping down as lead architect, to begin working with a group that would eventually form the majority of what Redfall Technologies Inc is today. Over the last 7 years I&#8217;ve had the opportunity to work with tremendous people doing what I enjoy.</p>
<p>As of January 10th, 2014 I&#8217;ve finalized my departure as a director and the CTO of Redfall Technologies to focus on other things. I&#8217;ve been working with Redfall over the last while to ensure a seamless transition. I still believe in Vogogo and will continue on as a Redfall shareholder and provide support whenever needed.</p>
<p>I wish Redfall all the best in the future.</p>
